If you prefer editing the config files directly, you can edit the file

~/.kde/share/config/kdeglobals</description><pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2013 21:30:55 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://faq.i3wm.org/question/915/how-to-edit-theme-of-kde-based-windows/?answer=1479#post-id-1479</guid></item></channel></rss>